  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators will study the efficacy and side effect profile of LGG, a probiotic, in
      pediatric patients with acute gastroenteritis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Multicenter randomized controlled trial of LGG in patients 3-48 months of age presenting to
      the Emergency Department with acute gastroenteritis.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
